OL,5,G2115 FIFA World Cup 2026: France v
OL,6,G     Sweden
OL,7,     FFrance v Sweden (Kick-off
OL,8,     F10.00pm). Coverage of the
OL,9,     Fround-of-32 match at New York/New
OL,10,     FJersey Stadium in the USA. France
OL,11,     Fare the tournament favourites,
OL,12,     Fafter an impressive group campaign
OL,13,     Fthat saw them win all three
OL,14,     Fmatches and score goals for fun,
OL,15,     Fincluding a 4-1 win against a
OL,16,     Fweakened Norway in their last
OL,17,     Fmatch. Sweden have produced a
OL,18,     Fmixed bag of results to progress
OL,19,     Fin third place from their group,
OL,20,     Fthrashing Tunisia, being hammered
OL,21,     Fby the Netherlands, and then
OL,22,     Fdrawing 1-1 to Japan, in a result
