OL,6,G     Ecuador
OL,7,     FMexico v Ecuador (Kick-off
OL,8,     F2.00am). Coverage of the
OL,9,     Fround-of-32 match at Mexico City
OL,10,     FStadium. Mexico were one of only
OL,11,     Fthree nations to win all three of
OL,12,     Ftheir group fixtures, giving them
OL,13,     Fhome advantage at a ground on
OL,14,     Fwhich they have an outstanding
OL,15,     Frecord. Ecuador progressed as one
OL,16,     Fof the third-placed qualifiers,
OL,17,     Flargely thanks to their 2-1 win
OL,18,     Fover Germany, which they did the
OL,19,     Fhard way, coming from a goal down
OL,20,     Fto finish on four points behind
OL,21,     Fthe Germans and Ivory Coast
